<view class="page">
  <view class="hero"><view class="eyebrow">KEEP A COPY</view><view class="title">数据备份</view><view class="subtitle">导出情侣空间的共享数据和你自己的私密数据，不会包含伴侣的私密记录。</view></view>
  <view class="panel panel--quiet">
    <view class="panel-title">导出前请注意</view>
    <view class="hint">导出的 JSON 可能包含敏感日期和文字。请保存在只有自己可以访问的位置，不要发送到公开群聊。</view>
  </view>
  <button class="button" loading="{{loading}}" disabled="{{loading}}" bindtap="copyExport">生成并复制备份</button>
  <view class="panel restore-panel">
    <view class="panel-title">从备份恢复</view>
    <view class="hint">只接受当前情侣空间生成的版本 1 备份。重复恢复会跳过；钱包流水和图片文件不会被导入。</view>
    <textarea value="{{backupText}}" maxlength="-1" placeholder="在此粘贴备份 JSON" bindinput="onBackupInput"></textarea>
    <button class="button secondary" loading="{{loading}}" disabled="{{loading || !backupText}}" bindtap="restoreBackup">校验并恢复记录与计划</button>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{summary}}" class="panel"><view class="status">备份已生成</view><view class="hint">{{summary}}</view></view>
  <view wx:if="{{error}}" class="error-banner">{{error}}</view>
</view>
